
- https://api.github.com/users/atoumi/repos is a Githtub API endpoint which list all repositories info of a user. In this is example is my user (atoumi).

- We will create a  playbook that download this file and save in our localhost.

Questions for this assignment
Create a play inside a playbook file that :

- Target the host "dev1"

- Download this link https://api.github.com/users/<USER>/repos ( replace <USER> by your github username or use my username "atoumi"  )

- Save the downloaded file in /tmp/git-repos.json file in the "localhost" NOT in "dev1".

